Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.08,0:00:07.48,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell me what room\NColonel Roy Mustang is staying in?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:09.23,Default,Nurse,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.91,0:00:12.49,Default,Nurse,0000,0000,0000,,May I have your name, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:15.16,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,The name's Nox. Doctor in private practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:17.41,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,He'll know right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:25.44,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:27.83,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:32.08,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Who might that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:34.32,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,I need him here for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.75,0:00:37.80,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,He's what I'd call my trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:42.56,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,So, is he down in the dumps?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:48.81,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,The main method of cultivation in the Ishbal area is double-cropping,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:50.71,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Bzzzt, try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:52.82,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,They raise the same crop semiannually.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:56.03,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,You expect to gain their trust like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:58.04,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.04,0:00:59.27,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Moving on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.27,0:01:01.95,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,So what crop do they raise with that method?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.54,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Barley and cotton.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:04.64,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:06.16,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,So you DO know your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.16,0:01:07.73,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.73,0:01:10.39,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I've been doing some research for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:15.30,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,He's planning to solve the Ishbalan crisis before becoming the Führer President.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:17.13,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,"Solving"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:20.64,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,But first things first, "becoming the Führer President"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:23.89,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Dr. Nox?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:25.85,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.24,0:01:29.40,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like... you're doing okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:30.63,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.63,0:01:32.75,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,These guys won't leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:34.08,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,No breaks, no nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.08,0:01:36.04,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Not exactly what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:37.60,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.15,0:01:38.86,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:44.62,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, it's the punishment Truth gave to someone who dreamt of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:46.37,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:49.77,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.14,0:01:53.37,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I can't stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:55.73,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Führer President...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:58.13,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to take care of Ishbal first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:01.15,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,The Ishbal Annihilation...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.19,0:02:04.14,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,That was what started everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:10.06,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Both for you, and for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:11.89,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to set things right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:12.93,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:15.89,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'm going to open up the areas in Ishbal that are currently off-limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.89,0:02:19.86,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'm going to allow the Ishbalans living in each slums back to their Holy Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:22.16,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,There's much more to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.71,0:02:27.55,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to overcome the crisis\Nthanks to Scar and the other people of Ishbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:30.32,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,We're in their debt, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:34.09,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel, I brought the data you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:38.59,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as if our sins will be forgiven,\Nbut we want to start with what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:43.24,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Christ, you lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:48.92,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, it looks like they took the words out of our mouths, Dr. Marcoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.08,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Marcoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:51.40,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Marcoh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:02:58.70,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.13,0:03:02.71,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a philosopher's stone right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:06.35,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,We should be able to get your vision back with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.21,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:18.71,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I made this stone in the past by using the lives of Ishbalans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:27.62,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I have no right to say this, but if it's for the sake of reviving Ishbal, I'm sure they'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:36.28,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,No, I cannot hear their voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:39.90,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a request from myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:44.74,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I want to patch you up with this stone for the sake of Ishbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:50.25,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,They might get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.79,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:58.75,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll gladly take your offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:02.73,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,And with that, I'll give it my all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:05.92,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:09.68,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,...there's someone who needs the power of the stone more than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:13.06,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I can come after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:25.28,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Havoc General Store, happily serving for 80 years now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.23,0:04:27.76,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Breda. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.15,0:04:32.90,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You want me to head down to Central NOW?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:36.95,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "you'll find out when you get there"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:42.90,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,How are your wounds treating you, Scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:45.46,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:48.97,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Initially to find out more about Eastern Alchemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:50.42,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,but the situation has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:55.67,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Mustang wants Miles for his new Ishbal policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:58.60,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I decided to take you along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:03.33,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Not as "Scar," but as someone of the Ishbalan race.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:06.30,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:08.93,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you help us in reviving the Ishbalan religion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:14.00,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot let a religion and a culture so rich in history die out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:17.00,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,The death of a culture equates to the death of its people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:21.00,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Save the people from death with your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:26.40,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,The meaning of being kept alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:31.04,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,So you want me to live for a bit longer to find what that is, huh, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.50,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.76,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.76,0:05:40.02,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Take me wherever you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:44.19,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Miles. I'm leaving the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:45.89,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Do things safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:46.70,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:48.91,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,That Mustang...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:53.52,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,He'd probably be frightened to death\Nif he were to find out that Scar is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:57.11,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:59.04,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,What is your true name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.69,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,I've died twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:09.30,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,I don't exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:12.88,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, I don't need a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:14.06,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Call me whatever you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.70,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:19.81,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet again, Ishbalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:35.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:40.08,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't imagine that my muscles would be this weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:42.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Want a ride on my back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:44.84,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:46.59,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I want to walk with my own two legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:53.02,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it slow, so you go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:56.01,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. We left the house together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:57.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go back together, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:04.73,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:07.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:14.80,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, your leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:19.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I haven't had maintenance on it in forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.67,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:25.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.48,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:28.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:30.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:35.85,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I wonder if Lin and the others have arrived in Xing already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:41.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's been two months since then, so I'm sure they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:45.31,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I hope May is okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:48.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave everything to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:56.61,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,May...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:58.45,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Al...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:00.30,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:01.79,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:04.62,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, the princess from the Chan clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:07.88,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Lin Yao!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:11.34,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, don't give me that scary look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:16.12,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:21.27,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you were unable to obtain a philosopher's stone because you were meddling in another country's affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:26.48,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,The Yao clan will now be in control.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:33.85,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,But don't fret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:37.35,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Our clan will protect yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:43.13,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man who even accepted the Homunculus Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:48.17,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accept the Chan clan along with all of the other clans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:55.24,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:09:00.09,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. People from Xing always keep promises, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:04.23,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,You'll "accept us all"? That's so greedy, Lin Yao!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:09.65,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, maybe he rubbed off on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:16.92,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then... guess we should start heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:18.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:19.21,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.91,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I want to give Fu a proper burial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:24.91,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:29.02,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:35.53,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,So many things happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:36.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Alphonse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:45.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like the princess of Xing,\NMay Chan, really took a liking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:47.48,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's such a nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:51.36,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Moving right along, what about things between you and Winry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:14.80,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Den! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:25.12,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Customers...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:37.48,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Den, that tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:11.66,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:13.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.08,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Good to be home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:28.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I suck at stuff like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:34.70,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:49.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:52.36,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, you still haven't fixed it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:56.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all worn out from greeting people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:58.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Winry knows that, but she's treating me like her slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:01.29,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:05.14,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,She wants you to come down for tea\Nnow that her apple pie is out of the oven.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:07.49,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:12.22,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We have a pretty amazing view today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:13.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:16.54,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The world is so vast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:17.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:23.36,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, there's something that's been on my mind for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:27.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm probably thinking of the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:35.66,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,How is your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:40.54,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many things to worry about; I feel like I suddenly aged twenty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:48.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But I have Mustang and Armstrong fulfilling their duties in the east and the north, respectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:52.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to them, an old geezer like me can somehow manage to perform my duties as the Führer President.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:55.14,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I really owe them a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:13:57.89,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not going to give away your position?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:03.31,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hand it over to the young ones just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:04.77,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:08.24,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,You sound just like my late husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:12.06,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,He was always totally committed to work, like you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:15.59,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I'm the most...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:20.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,...irresponsible person I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:27.00,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, Selim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:28.13,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:30.95,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,This little birdy is hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:31.97,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Could you help him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:35.64,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:38.52,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,Have the butler call a veterinarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:41.35,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Will... Will he get better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:43.94,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.86,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,Run along now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:49.77,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He's grown into such a kind boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:51.26,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,He has.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:56.29,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone protested when I decided I'd raise him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.61,0:14:59.36,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,but he's grown so much without giving me reason to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:03.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be keeping an eye on him for just a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:11.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're aware what we'll have to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:16.39,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,...if he causes trouble, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:19.64,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:30.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A homunculus and a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:34.65,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Will they really be able to understand each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:41.33,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,New possibilities get you excited no matter how old you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:50.22,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,Is Edward not depressed about his left leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:51.88,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:56.92,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,He even said, "As punishment, I'd rather keep my leg as an automail."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:57.93,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:02.69,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,He also said, "Winry'll cry if I don't have this."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:05.94,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:12.24,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you two got your bodies back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:15.07,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Maes will be happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:21.98,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Starting with Mr. Hughes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:29.49,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,So many different people from so many different places helped us be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:33.89,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why I feel like it's our turn to give back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:37.14,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you alchemists call "Equivalent Exchange"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:42.02,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. If we received 10 and gave 10 back,\Neverything would be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:47.17,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,If we receive 10, we add an extra and give back 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:51.60,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It's very minor, but it's a new rule my brother and I came up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:56.53,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But now we're going to have to live up to our word.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:17:00.03,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,There's something you want to do, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:05.53,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,There's a girl we couldn't save.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:10.55,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We still can't forget about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:15.34,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.35,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jerso, Mr. Zampano.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:18.11,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:19.75,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a ton of food. Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:20.73,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:24.15,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Can I get a glass of milk and a sandwich?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:25.02,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:30.98,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you've already paid your respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:32.32,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:33.89,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:34.49,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,...time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:37.24,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to Xing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:42.80,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I plan on studying Eastern Alchemy full-scale at May's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:44.27,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Not just Xing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:48.88,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go around all the eastern countries to study various things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:52.76,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see and learn many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:54.58,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I also want to meet many new people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:59.76,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But wait, are you two really coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:01.59,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:03.26,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Our wild instincts tell us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:06.39,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,...that coming along with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:09.56,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...will get us something great!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:14.65,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Alphonse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:18.61,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to look for a way to return to our old bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:21.29,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who told us not to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:24.12,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do things ourselves\Ninstead of having others do the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:26.62,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:29.96,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't your brother coming to Xing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:31.11,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:35.25,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking the eastern route,\Nand he's taking the western route.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:38.88,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,And once the two of us gather the knowledge we gained from both directions,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:42.60,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,we may be able to avoid the same kind of tragedy that happened to Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:45.25,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:48.77,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the only reason why we're traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:54.30,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We want to see just how vast the world is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:57.47,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,You need to oil it every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:18:58.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:19:00.67,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,And check to make sure all the screws are tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:01.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:04.20,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Dry it off after coming out of the shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:06.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:08.28,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you even listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:09.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:10.50,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:16.52,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:26.28,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,With this attitude, you're just going to end up\Nbreaking it and having to come back again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:29.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:33.51,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,When you need maintenance,\Nbe sure to call in for an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:34.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:41.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Appointment...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:49.54,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:53.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Winry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:57.46,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Just speak up if you've got something to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:05.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's equivalent exchange!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:10.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you half of my life, so you give me half of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.87,0:20:22.43,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:25.02,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Why do alchemists have to be like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:28.00,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,"Equivalent Exchange"? Are you retarded?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:29.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:31.23,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,You really are stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:33.50,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Half? I'll give you all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:44.80,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, maybe not all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:45.74,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,90 percent...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:47.71,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe.. 80 percent?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:49.42,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,A bit more than 70...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:50.49,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, 85 percent?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:52.81,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! I can give you that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:56.10,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:57.63,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:00.09,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,My bad, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:02.61,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Ed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:06.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You really are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:10.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're able to overturn the law of equivalent exchange so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:12.76,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:14.12,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:15.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:22.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That cheered me up. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.91,0:21:24.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:30.00,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:49.05,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, even Edward left on a trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:52.29,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't they settle down a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.59,0:21:54.54,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,For them, this is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:21:59.02,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Men who keep still are no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.27,0:22:04.80,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A lesson without pain is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.78,0:22:10.75,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,That's because no one can gain without sacrificing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.77,0:22:16.67,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But by enduring that pain and overcoming it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:22.03,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,...he shall obtain a powerful, unmatched heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:26.21,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A fullmetal heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.21,0:22:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
